Title: Precisely, My Brow Pencil Ultra-Fine Brow Defining Pencil
Description:
Transform shapeless, undefined brows with just a few strokes of Benefit's bestselling precisely, my brow pencil. The custom ultra-fine tip makes adding detailed definition to your brows easy, by drawing incredibly natural-looking, hair like strokes that last up to 12-hours.* This rich, waterproof** eyebrow pencil is ideal for spot filling sparse or over-tweezed areas, and the smudge-proof formula is firm enough for precise application, yet glides on effortlessly to bring symmetry to your brows and your entire face.

How to Apply:
Hold the pencil along the custom control grip
To shape brows, use longer, horizontal strokes along the base of your brow
Fill by drawing short, upward strokes in the direction of your natural hair growth
Gently brush through brows with the Spoolie to evenly blend color & tame hairs

Transform shapeless, undefined brows with just a few strokes of Benefit's bestselling precisely, my brow pencil. The custom ultra-fine tip makes adding detailed definition to your brows easy, by drawing incredibly natural-looking, hair like strokes that last up to 12-hours.* This rich, waterproof** eyebrow pencil is ideal for spot filling sparse or over-tweezed areas, and the smudge-proof formula is firm enough for precise application, yet glides on effortlessly to bring symmetry to your brows and your entire face.

How to Apply:
Hold the pencil along the custom control grip
To shape brows, use longer, horizontal strokes along the base of your brow
Fill by drawing short, upward strokes in the direction of your natural hair growth
Gently brush through brows with the Spoolie to evenly blend color & tame hairs

An invisible foundation that creates a natural healthy glow by giving skin the radiance of a day spent outdoors, while protecting it from harsh environmental conditions.

Title: Capture Totale C.E.L.L. Energy Firming & Wrinkle-Correcting Creme
Description: Re-energize your skin with Dior's new innovative patented Bio-Cellular Technology to help refine, smooth, enhance suppleness and firm the appearance skin. This age-defying cream was born from Dior's 20 years of research on mother cells and its floral expertise, for more resilient, youthful and healthy glowing skin. Your skin's youthful radiance is determined by just 0.2% of your skin cells: mother cells. Over time, these precious cells lose half their energy potential. Dior's science has developed a patented Bio-Cellular Technology that helps restore the energy power of the skin's precious mother cells. Description:
Christian Dior Capture Totale Multi-Perfection Creme Universal Texture has the following features:
The Multi-Perfection Creme circumvents the laws of time and, for the 1st time, those of gravity.
This creme encourages the revitalization of the skin's precious 'springs': the mother cells at the origin of the deep contouring of the skin.
Superbly smoothing, resculpting and unifying, it tones the skin from its deepest layers to its surface.
The face is perfectly tautened and toned while all visible signs of aging - wrinkles, loss of firmness and radiance, and uneven skin tone - are corrected instantly and with every application.
Youthful beauty is brought to its pinnacle. Today and tomorrow.
With its fine, delicate, melt-in texture for unrivaled sensory delight, the Multi-Perfection Creme Universal texture delivers an instant embellishing effect and optimal comfort for all women.
Chez Dior.

Global youthful beauty: Smoothed fine lines and wrinkles +85%, Firmer skin +97%, Redensified skin +95%

Title: Colour 2-In-1 Prime & Colour Correct Face-Eyes-Lips
Description:
Christian Dior Fix It Colour 2-In-1 Prime & Colour Correct Face-Eyes-Lips has the following features:
Dior invents its first multipurpose colour concealer: 1 stick, 2 textures, 3 application areas, 4 expert shades, targeting and neutralizing the colour imperfections of the complexion and around the eye and lip contours with the inspiration of backstage makeup techniques.

Blue (100):
Target the dullness.
This lilac-blue is an expert on yellow-toned Caucasian skins and Asian skins by evening out exhausted complexions for extra radiance.
Dab on the light-catching areas such as the forehead and the tips of the cheeks to give them an instantly fresh and rested look.

Apricot (200):
Ideal for matte or tanned complexions.
Tones down greyness, diminishes dark spots and corrects areas of hyperpigmentation and dark circles, while evening out dark skins.

Yellow (300): 
Targets the dark spots and dark circles.
A must-have for light skins to erase violet-tinted shadows, from blood vessels to circles under the eyes.
Neutralizes lips with a blue hue to bring out the real colour of the lipstick.

Green (400): 
Target the redness.
Used in light touches to fade blood vessels and flushed areas to target light complexions and rosy skins.

Title: Super Restorative Day Cream
Description:
Clarins Super Restorative Day Cream (For Very Dry Skin), with its illuminating, lifting and replenishing formula, helps restore elasticity to mature skin challenged by natural hormonal changes due to the ageing process. Clarins has discovered that a cell in the dermis called Fibroblast plays a key part in maintaining youthful skin.

When the function of Fibroblast is disrupted, the skin ageing process speeds up. Clarins Super Restorative Day Cream (For Very Dry Skin) is infused with Harungana plant extract, which can reactivate deprived Fibroblast and stimulate growth of collagen fibres. Combined with new generation line-filling pearls, skin appears plumped and tighter immediately, and deep wrinkles are reduced.

Clarins Super Restorative Day Cream (For Very Dry Skin) is also added with Vitamin C derivative that inhibits melanin production to minimize the appearance of age spots, thus achieving a more illuminated and even complexion. Hyaluronic Acid and Shea Butter moisturize skin, restoring a comfortable, supple feel.

Title: All About Shadow Quad
Description:
A versatile, long-wearing eye shadow palette featuring crease- and fade-resistant shades. Wear each shadow on its own or blend them together for a signature look. The quad comes complete with a mirrored compact, two sponge-tip applicators and illustrated how-to's, so application is a breeze.

How to use: Use the applicator to sweep an allover base shade across your entire eyelid, from your lashline to your brow bone. Create dimension with medium-toned shades. Layer and blend color into the crease or along the lashline. The deepest shade can be applied as a liner along your lashline using the applicator tip. Remove with your favorite makeup remover.

Description:
A new formula, Clinique Repairwear Laser Focus Smoothes, Restores, Corrects is an award-winning serum that is clinically tested to bring a striking reduction in lines and wrinkles in as little as 4 weeks. Oil-free formula suitable for all skin types.

Inspired by the femininity of Sicilian women, Miss Sicily is the first colour and care lipstick of Dolce & Gabbana, that delivers the colour of a lipstick, the shine of a gloss, and the care of a balm.

The ideal on-the-go lipstick for an effortless application.
Long-lasting comfort with ultra-light texture.

Buildable colour payoff.
Unique blend of pigments and polymers for colored radiance with a dewy finish.

Title: The Foundation Perfect Luminous Liquid Foundation
Description:
Dolce & Gabbana The Foundation Perfect Luminous Liquid Foundation has the following features:
Subtly highlights skin with golden reflections for a flawless, dewy finish with this sophisticated, fluid foundation.
Reflects the light for a radiant glow with illuminating powders.
Infused with moisturising ingredients, it gives skin a silky look and feel.
With light to medium buildable coverage.
Wide range of shades to suit all skin tones from pale to darker complexions.
Ideal for those seeking a smooth, satin-like look with translucent coverage.
Fragrance-free.
Suitable for all skin types.

Title: Passion Duo Gloss Fusion Lipstick
Description:
Dolce & Gabbana Passion Duo Gloss Fusion Lipstick has the following features:
Combines a layer of intense colour with a heart of satin gloss.
The smooth formula offers exceptional glamour and seamless wearability from day to night with a diverse bouquet of shades.
Combines long-lasting colour with a super-glossy shine with this two-in-one lipstick.
Offers effortless application that one coat gives double the results.
Infused with skin-conditioning ingredients and moisturisers, it hydrates and softens lips.
Offers buildable colour with innovative formula.
Available in a variety of vivid and versatile colour combinations.
Targeted for the woman desiring long-lasting lip colour with a full gloss shine.

Title: Cleanser
Description:
The EVE LOM Cleanser was described by Vogue as ‚Ëœprobably the best cleanser in the world and is the foundation of our skincare regime. It changed the face of cleansing and continues to, everywhere in the world we launch, being expertly balanced for all skin types, skin concerns and environmental conditions. With its signature blend of four aromatic plant oils, specially woven 100% cotton Muslin Cloth and quick routine, the result is incredibly glowing, radiant skin with a smoother, more refined texture. The difference can be seen instantly and just keeps on improving with use.

Benefits:

Deep cleanses without drying or stripping the skin and removes even the most stubborn of waterproof make-up

Thorough cleansing and gentle exfoliation enables skin cells to regenerate quickly and provides a vital receptive base for beauty products to work at their best

Decongests and with the signature massage technique helps drain toxins

Exfoliates, tones, improves circulation when combined with the specially woven Muslin Cloth

Softens and conditions the skin

Description:

The stop-everything, give-it-to-me lip gloss that feels as good as it looks. Fenty Beauty Gloss Bomb Universal Lip Luminizer delivers explosive shine, now in six universal shades handpicked by Rihanna herself to be the ultimate finishing touch to any look.

Title: Facial Patches for Wrinkles on the Forehead & Between Eyes
Description:
Anti-Aging Facial Patches Smooth Wrinkles While You Sleep

Without any harsh chemicals or needles FROWNIES Facial Patches for Wrinkles assist to soften and smooth wrinkles mechanically. Designed to provide lasting results with continued use. FROWNIES Facial Patches for Wrinkles addresses the physical cause of facial wrinkles between the eyes (sometimes called elevens) and forehead wrinkles. By holding the crease flat and relaxed while you sleep the body can relax muscle memory. The muscles of the face cannot move under the patch, keeping you from frowning or expressing while you sleep.

This is Frownies 100 year old anti-wrinkle secret. The secret of Frownies has been passed along by generations of women and men in entertainment and the public eye who rely on this amazingly effective method to maintain a youthful appearance. FROWNIES Facial Patches are the safe, natural way to dramatically reduce or eliminate expression lines and creases by relaxing and retraining facial muscles while you sleep.
Tags/catagories/collections: Less than $50

Title: Facial Patches for Wrinkles on the Corners of Eyes & Mouth
Description:
Avoid Wrinkle Fillers - Smooth Wrinkles While You Sleep. Wrinkle Treatment for Corners of Eyes and Mouth (Crow's Feet)

Smiling, speaking and just talking produces lines from the corner of the nose to the corner of the mouth in some women. When this muscle is pushed back away from the mouth the cheeks and lips lose support creating what are sometime called marionette lines. FROWNIES Facial Patches for Wrinkles on the Corners of Eyes & Mouth is used to splint these lines to improve the appearance of the area around the mouth.

Before crow's feet at the corner of the eyes become deep, stop them with Facial Patches for Wrinkles on the Corners of Eyes & Mouth. These lines start as dry skin that loses its' elasticity.

Description:
Giorgio Armani Power Fabric Longwear High Cover Foundation SPF25 has the following features:
A new liquid foundation that teams full coverage with an ultra-light formula.
Delivers three stunning features for a long-lasting, lightweight complexion with high coverage.
A concentration of oils with no greasy effect, which delivers a velvet matte finish.

Title: Le Rouge Perfecto Beautifying Lip Balm
Description:
Givenchy Le Rouge Perfecto Beautifying Lip Balm has the following features:
Lip balm reinvented a moisturizer, plumper and color enhancer, it is a new couture lip care for naturally sublime lips.
The 3-in-1 formula combines plumping and moisturizing ingredients with a sheer wash of natural color for lovely, glowy lips.
Innovative Lip replumper complex provides an incredible instant-plump effect.
A melting texture with shea extract leaves lips highly moisturized.
Features a magic ingredient that reacts to your lips pH for a natural made-to-measure result: a rosy color unique to you!
With its rose-colored, genuine leather case, this is the new couture care for a fresh and natural look.

Instantly mattifies the complexion with long lasting hold, while keeping skin balanced and allowing it to breathe.

Title: Teint Couture Balm Blurring Foundation Balm SPF15 - PA++
Description:
Givenchy Teint Couture Balm Blurring Foundation Balm SPF15 - PA++ has the following features:
A complexion-enhancing veil that blurs and brightens your skin tone. 
Formulated with blurring technology to smooth and unify your complexion and create a subtle second skin effect. 
Light-reflecting diamond powder pigments enrich your skin tone with a gorgeous glow, resulting in a beautifully fresh finish for up to 12 hours. 
Light & Blur complex erases the look of imperfections on your skin, whilst diffusing fine lines and wrinkles. 
Hydro-magnets work to lock in moisture to your complexion, preventing your skin from feeling and looking dehydrated. 
Antioxidants, vitamin E and jasmine flower nourish your skin whilst protecting your skin from free radicals. 
This delicate formula melts into your skin with a non-greasy feel.

Title: Rouge Interdit Vinyl Extreme Shine Lipstick Illicit Color
Description:
Givenchy Rouge Interdit Vinyl Extreme Shine Lipstick Illicit Color has the following features:
The new lip beauty secret for women. A lipstick so addictive and so illicit, it's almost forbidden.
A unique lipstick that dares everything: extreme shine, impactful shades, and an obvious plump-up effect.
It is more than a lipstick, it is an attitude. It provides the signature look for beauty addicts who are not afraid to assert their own rules of style.

An amazing stretch formula for lips with tantalizing curves.
Lips instantly appear fuller and smoother with intense color.
The slick case has metallic satin ribbon inspired by the House fashion designs.

Title: Orchidée Impériale Black The Cream (Refill)
Description:
fter more than 15 years of research, the Orchidarium and Guerlain Research present Orchidée Impériale Black The Cream, a masterpiece of Guerlain skincare featuring the extraordinary properties of the Black Orchid. Originally from Peru, this rare orchid increases its longevity by adapting to its environment. Like a talisman in the combat against time, the Black Orchid has given rise to the BlackimmuneTM technology, Each application helps the skin better withstand internal and external stresses and reduce the visible signs of ageing. The Cream helps minimize wrinkles, refine the skin texture and lend definition to facial contours, leaving the skin feeling firmer and suppler as well as looking radiant.

Title: Terracotta Matte Sculpting Powder
Description:
This sun-kissed powder warms the complexion and sculpts the features. Soft and easy to apply, its comfortable, ultra-fine texture blends with the skin to build the result up to the desired intensity. Enriched with Kaolin, a white clay known for its mattifying properties, the matte powder sculpts the complexion with a shine-free finish.
How To Apply Sculpting Powder: Apply the sculpting powder with a brush, tracing a "3" on each side of the face, from the forehead to just under the cheekbones, from under the cheekbones to the chin, finishing with a stroke down the neck.

Title: The Longevity Concentrate
Description:
Guerlain Orchidee Imperiale The Longevity Concentrate has the following features:
It targets the areas where youthful volume has been lost, for redensified, radiant skin.
The highly concentrated Cell RespirationT technology regulates the level of oxygen in the skin cells. The cells can breathe again and maximize energy production which boosts cell regeneration for reducing the signs of ageing.
It also combined with the redensifying action of a natural origin ingredient, tigernut extract which strengthens the structure and cohesion of the fibres supporting the skin.
The skin perfecting effect is down to the action of a rose hip extract that minimizes the pores.

Description:

Title: Orchidee Imperiale Black La Cure The Treatment
Description:
Guerlain Orchidee Imperiale Black La Cure The Treatment has the following features:
Based on four complementary formulas, one for each week, it gives an exceptional efficiency boost to visibly renew the aspect of the skin within a month.
Powered with Blackimmune technology and a combination of ultra-powerful ingredients, this provides the skin with ultimate self-protection and comprehensive age-defying performance for an extraordinary youthful appearance.
WEEK I: Resurface
The skin looks like it has been renewed, while dead cells are eliminated and the texture of the skin is more refined.
Wrinkles and fine lines seem to fade away, leaving skin incredibly smooth.

WEEK II: Illuminate
The skin regains its original radiance whilst the complexion is more even.

WEEK III: Redefine
Facial contours appear more distinct and the jaw-line is redefined and the skin is visibly denser and firmer.

WEEK IV: Plump
Perfectly nourished, the skin is suppler and plumper, and contours are redefined.
The skin is velvety to the touch and flawless.

Description:

With a single stroke, it offers a perfect application and pay-off instantly.

Title: Meteorites Light Revealing Pearls of Powder
Description:
Guerlain Meteorites Light Revealing Pearls of Powder is a reinvention of the iconic Meteorites Perles for its Spring 2014 Meteorites Blossom collection. Incorporating Guerlain's exclusive Stardust Technology, each pearl contains a spherical light-creating polymer, which transforms light invisible to the naked eye into a pure and endless glow on the skin.

A subtle blend of matte, rosy and radiant blue-toned white pearls, combined with corrective coloured pearls yellow to counter redness, pink for freshness and mauve to catch the light Guerlain Meteorites Light Revealing Pearls of Powder light up the face in an illuminating and corrective halo to give endless radiance.

Title: Liquid Minerals Foundation - Amber
Description:
Jane Iredale Liquid Minerals Foundation is a light-reflecting, soft-focus foundation with beads encapsulating skin-nourishing ingredients that work in a time-released action. The spheres include Hyaluronate Acid and Olive Squalene that are entrapped by seaweed lipids, which are then suspended in an Aloe Vera and Lavender Flower gel.

Suitable for all skin types, Jane Iredale Liquid Minerals A Foundation makes skin look more youthful, diminishes the appearance of lines and wrinkles, minimizes pores, and evens out skin tone. It has a natural pH of 6 and is so perfectly balanced that it needs no pH adjusters.

As Jane Iredale Liquid Minerals Foundation is applied and worked into the skin, the body temperature breaks down the liposomes so that they can release their actives in a prolonged time-release action for the ultimate in skin health and protection.
Tags/catagories/collections: Brands, clearance, Face Makeup, Foundation, Jane Iredale, Less than $50, Makeup, xpromo25

Title: Dermatologist Solutions Clearly Corrective Dark Spot Solution
Description:
Kiehl's Dermatologist Solutions Clearly Corrective Dark Spot Solution with exclusive activated C, Clearly Corrective is a fast-acting serum that evens skin tone and diminishes dark spots to impart overall radiance and luminosity to the skin.

With continued daily usage, Clearly Corrective helps to prevent the formation of future dark spots and other skin discolorations.
In as little as 2 weeks, 55% of women clinically demonstrated a significant reduction in dark spot intensity.

In 4 weeks, 69% of women clinically demonstrated a continued reduction in dark spots intensity and 73% of women showed a significant reduction in acne scarring. Reduction in other skin discolorations was clinically evident among 69% of women.

In 8 weeks, 87% of women clinically demonstrated more uniform skin tone to deliver breakthrough clarity.

Title: Midnight Recovery Concentrate
Description:
Kiehl's Midnight Recovery Concentrate is a natural replenishing elixir of pure botanical oils that provides vital nutrients to enhance skin's nighttime recovery. One night. Two drops. Younger-looking skin by morning.

Kiehl's Midnight Recovery Concentrate works with the skin's natural nocturnal activity when skin is most receptive to repairing itself from daily aggressors to dramatically restore skin. Enriched with Squalane, a botanical lipid similar in molecular structure to natural skin lipids, Evening Primrose Oil, rich in Omega-6 Fatty Acids and Essential Oils inlcuding Lavenderour formula provides a boost of intensive moisture to depleted skin. These natural oils instantly penetrate the skin surface to help replenish it. 99.8% naturally-derived and paraben-free.

Title: Lifting Primer Serum
Description:
La Mauve Lifting Primer Serum has the following features:
This first serum combines various cutting-edge, highly effective ingredients which lift, firm, hydrate and brighten your skin, restoring a younger and radiant look and reversing the signs of aging.
SEPILIFT™ DPHP, a patented comprehensive anti-aging ingredient, one of the most powerful of its kind in the 21st century, boosts wrinkle-smoothing, lifting and moisturizing effects. It triggers collagen remodeling and collagen fiber contraction for instant lifting and firming, smoothing different kinds of fine lines.
Infused with highly ingenious Snow Algae Powder, which are able to survive the extreme conditions of alpine and polar snow fields. The valuable stress response molecules produced under these extreme environmental conditions can protect the youthfulness of skin effectively.
Snow Algae Powder activates biochemical pathways that are essential key factors in a promising longevity theory: the calorie restriction. Calorie restriction, a special dietary regime reduces calorie intake by between 25% and 65%, has been shown in many experiments to improve both the health span and lifespan of individuals.
Snow Algae Powder improves the longevity of skin cells by mimicking the effects of caloric restriction. It activates two key factors of the calorie restriction pathway: the Klotho longevity gene and the AMPK energy sensor.
The activation of these two pathways leads to improved cellular defenses, cell detoxification and repair, thus helping to stimulate collagen production, rejuvenate the dermal-epidermal junction, reduce dark spots and reinforce skin barrier for a younger, smoother look.
Swiss Alps Lipobelle Glacier delivers incomparable and long-lasting hydrating effect, protecting skin against heat-stress effects and providing 24 hour hydration. The glacier water is encapsulated by lecithin molecules to ensure it is carried into the deeper layers of the epidermis.
Oligo-HA is an ultra-low molecular weight hyaluronic acid, which is designed for better skin penetration. It promotes blood circulation, improves skin metabolism, smoothes wrinkles effectively and increases skin elasticity.
Fucogel forms a bio elastic film on the skin, bringing ultimate moisture and softness to the skin as well as a pleasant sensation.

Sheer, buildable coverage lets you customize your glow.

Bronzer: Using the Bronzer Brush, lightly tap on top of domed bronzer, making sure to cover all edges of brush with product. Tap off excess product. Using the tapered head of the brush, apply to areas where the sun naturally hits, like cheeks, nose, brow bone, forehead and chin, creating a natural """"sun-kissed"""" look.

Highlighter: Using the Angled Cheek Colour brush, lightly tap onto domed highlighter covering all edges of brush. Tap off excess product. Using the tapered head of the brush, apply over the high points of the face: cheekbones, center of nose, cupid's bow and top of forehead.

Title: Mask
Description:
Luxriche Mask has the following features:
A lifting mask that contains 42ml rich beauty ingredients for tightening and firming cheeks for beautiful face contour.
The ear hook design plus lower part mask that covers the jaw allows ingredients to penetrate sufficiently into the entire face. The moment you remove the mask, your skin will feel more lifted and tensed beyond experience.
Added with Hydrolyzed Egg Shell Membrane, a Type III collagen that is responsible for skin’s elasticity and exists in baby’s skin, for plump and elastic skin.
Syn-Ake (Dipeptide Diaminobutyroyl Benzylamide Diacetate) with its -like effect, helps smooth persistent wrinkles such as those along nasolabial folds.
Escin boosts 5 benefits of water drainage, anti-inflammatory, whitening, promoting blood circulation, and balancing skin.
A blend of rich complexes of Butcher's Broom Root Extract, Licorice Root, Centella Asiatica Extract, hydrolyzed yeast protein, and Calendula Officinalis Flower Extract helps carry away waste materials that cause sagging and swelling, and regain skin firmness. Also, it repairs skin damage by stimulus and prevents pigmentation.
Peptide provides skin with nutrients to increase firmness and sooth wrinkles.
Pro vitamin B5 activates the metabolism of skin cells and rejuvenates your skin.

Title: Shampoo
Description:
Orofluido Shampoo cleanses delicately, conserving the hair's structure and leaving it light and incredibly shiny. Orofluido Shampoo is the beauty treatment for all hair types that delicately cleanses to leave hair light and shiny. A pure luxuriance that envelops the hair.

Orofluido is pure sensuality, a celebration of the senses. The mystery of the fragrance of amber, the fascination for the most precious natural oils. The luxury of gold. A beauty ritual for all types of hair. Its delicious amber fragrance with a vanilla foundation will transport you into a fascinating world of oriental perfume.

An exquisite mixture of natural oils:
Argan oil: liquid gold for your hair
Extracted from the seeds of the Argania spinosa fruit, Argan oil is rich in vitamin E and essential fatty oils, similar in composition to our own skin. It strengthens hair and makes it extremely light and incredibly silky.

Linseed oil: instant shine
The seeds of the linen plant are the source of a precious oil which seals and smoothes the hair cuticle, providing uniformity and control. The result is hair that captures and reflects the light, giving it a spectacular shine.

Cyperus oil: pure silk to the touch
Cyperus is a plant that has been cultivated in Egypt for more than 4,000 years. It is the source of an oil with a high content of fatty acids and tocopherol, which give natural protection against free radicals. It provides softness and volume, leaving hair manageable, smooth and flexible.

Title: Genoptics Aura Essence
Description:
SK-II GenOptics Aura Essence has the following features:
This all-new upgraded whitening formula contains Pixel white ,De-melano P3C, Japanese UME extract, Concentrated PITERA and new ingredients including US Prunus Extract and Inositol. They work together to help improve lackluster and dull skin, reduces spots and UV-induced melanin for a radiant complexion.
After using for 8 weeks, it significantly improves dull skin, increases melanin-blocking substances, and reduces colored pigments deep in the skin for clearer, more radiant and translucent skin.
Effectively reduces spots deep in the skin and restores diamond-like radiance and brightness to skin.
Lightweight texture, feels hydrating on the skin and instantly illuminates skin.
Smart dropper design allows the dropper to get the recommended dosage automatically every time, as you twist and open the bottle, and just the right amount for the whole face.
GenOptics Spot Essence is ideal for day use, while GenOptics Aura Essence is suitable for night use. Using both products will complement each other and achieve even better results.

Title: Genoptics Spot Essence
Description:
SK-II GenOptics Spot Essence has the following features:

Title: Genoptics Spot Essence
Description:
SK-II GenOptics Spot Essence has the following features:
This all-new upgraded whitening formula contains the latest Spot Resist Complex, which includes Lumina Kelp Extract, a new ingredient that effectively slows down the transmission of melanin message in the skin.
Also contains Concentrated PITERA and De-melano P3C, this treatment reduces colored pigments on the surface and inside the skin, as well as minimizing the formation of future pigments.
After using it for 6 weeks, it significantly decreases stubborn pigments and future invisible spots in the epidermis, revealing translucent and flawless skin.
Effectively reduces spots deep in the skin and restores diamond-like radiance and brightness to skin.
Lightweight texture, feels fresh on the skin and easily absorbed.
Smart dropper design allows the dropper to get the recommended dosage automatically every time, as you twist and open the bottle, and just the right amount for the whole face.
GenOptics Spot Essence is ideal for day use, while GenOptics Aura Essence is suitable for night use. Using both products will complement each other and achieve even better results.

Title: R.N.A.Power Essence Serum
Description:
SK-II R.N.A Radical New Age Essence has the following features:
The latest anti-aging range, this essence brings you the next level of firmness - lengthwise and crosswise - for poreless, plump skin with a fresh morning glow.
Immediately upon application, each drop penetrates deep into your skin, making it firmer, more resilient, and feeling plumper.
Skin becomes smooth and tinged with a fresh morning glow the next day.
One bottle reduces the appearance of pores and wrinkles.
Clinical studies show that in just 1 night, pores become small; after 10 days, skin becomes more elastic; after 28 days, skin is supple and smooth.
Used with R.N.A Power cream, this new duo from SK-II brings you to a new level of confidence from today and for the next 15 years.

Title: R.N.A. Power Face Cream
Description:
A bestselling moisturizing cream to supercharge your skin's youthful radiance.

Solutions for:
- Fine lines and wrinkles
- Loss of firmness and elasticity
- Dullness and uneven texture

Packed with nourishing ingredients, this velvety moisturizer restores skin suppleness and elasticity with intense hydration. Inspired by award-winning science, this advanced formula combines SK-II's Radical New Age (R.N.A.) complex with signature ingredient pitera, a bio-ingredient that helps renew skin, boost moisture and radiance, and combat signs of aging.

Title: Correct & Perfect All-In-One Color Correcting Palette
Description:
Create Complexion Perfection!

Under-eye circles, redness, uneven or dull skin? Not anymore with this all-in-one customizable color correcting palette. Five velvety smooth cream color correctors and two tinted setting powders are all you need to help neutralize imperfections and brighten dull skin tones.

Cream Correctors:

Peach – neutralizes dark under-eye circles on fair/medium skin tones
Pink – brightens eye area and masks fatigue
Yellow – neutralizes hyperpigmentation and dark spots
Green – counteracts redness (i.e. from rosacea, acne, broken capillaries, and sunburn)
Orange – counteracts dark under-eye circles on darker skin tones; also neutralizes veins

Pressed Setting Powders: 

Yellow – sets any correcting cream or can be used allover to even out skin tone
Lavender – sets pink correcting cream or can be used allover to brighten sallow/yellow skin


Benefits:

Five lightweight, sheer to medium, buildable colored creams and two tinted translucent finishing powders allow for customized coverage.
Specially formulated with nourishing vitamins A, C and E and Arclay Youth Revival Bio-Available Mineral Complex™ to help diminish the appearance of pores and fine lines, moisturize and control oil
Long-wearing, waterproof
Easy to master! Includes a user-friendly booklet filled with makeup artist inspired tips and tricks.
Tags/catagories/collections: Brands, Color Correct, Face Makeup, Makeup, Stila

Title: One Step Correct Skin Tone Correcting & Brightening Primer
Description:
Swirl your way to perfect skin in one step! This innovative, triple-swirled helix serum instantly primes, color-corrects, brightens and nourishes skin for a flawless face with no fuss.

The revolutionary product contains 3 color-correcting pigments to even out complexion:

Green tone instantly neutralizes redness and conceals blemishes
Lavender tone counteracts sallow undertones for a vibrant, energized look
Peach tone brightens, illuminates and helps diminish the appearance of sun spots


Supercharged with Stila's proprietary Youth Revival Bio-Available Mineral Complex to help hydrate, control oil, and diminish the appearance of pores and fine lines.

Title: Mascara
Description:
A mascara so amazing, it's... Better Than Sex!

Too Faced's hourglass-shaped brush was designed after discovering the bust-waist-hip ratio of an iconic silver screen blonde bombshell held the secret to the perfect brush silhouette that separates, coats and curls each lash to voluptuous perfection. One coat of the carbon black formula and lashes are full, defined, and stretched to unbelievable lengths.

Benefits:
  • The #1-selling prestige mascara in America*
  • Film-forming polymers lock curl in place
  • Acacia Senegal Tree Extract sets volume
  • Hourglass-shaped brush helps coat every lash
  • Peptides condition lashes
  • Vegan friendly
  • Cruelty free
Tags/catagories/collections: Brands, Eye Makeup, Makeup, Mascara, Too Faced

Title: Papa Don't Peach Peach-Infused Blush
Description:
This burst of sweet peachy-bronze adds a fresh youthful radiance to cheeks for a summertime warmth.

Infused with the skin-loving essence of peach
Smells like peaches
Rich, pigmented shade provides buildable payoff
Complements any skin tone
Brightening finish from gilded pink pearl
How to use:
Add definition to the hollows of the cheeks with a matte bronzer then pop Papa Don't Peach Blush on the apples of the cheeks for a warm radiant finish
Use with Sweet Peach Eye Shadow Collection, Sweet Peach Creamy Lip Oil
Cruelty-Free

Title: Melted Matte Liquified Matte Long Wear Lipstick
Description: Long-wearing, innovative ultra-matte lipstick with the staying power of a stain and the intense color of a liquid lipstick. Melted Matte ensures color always looks rich, full, and kissable never dry, shriveled, or cracked.
Tags/catagories/collections: Brands, Lips, Lipstick, Liquid Lipstick, Makeup, Too Faced

Title: Hangover Replenishing Face Primer
Description:
Got a beauty hangover? Too Faced's replenishing face primer is your instant cure. It hydrates, smoothes and brightens skin for a dewy, healthy looking finish.

When long days of work and late nights of play give you a beauty hangover, this is your instant cure. Hangover is a revolutionary makeup primer infused with coconut water, probiotics and skin revivers that work together to boost skin's radiance, promote elasticity and help hydrate while locking down makeup for fresher, longer and more flawless wear.

Too Faced harnessed the science of hydration to create a creamy, penetrating primer that acts like an energy drink for the skin by replenishing moisture levels. It can be worn alone for a dewy, healthy looking finish or under bronzers, foundations and powders to create the perfect canvas.

More To Love:
Hydrate and brighten skin
Promote skin's elasticity and tone
Soothe and smooth the skin
Get all the priming benefits you love while looking like you received eight hours of sleep and drank your daily dose of H2O
Paraben free
Cruelty free
Vegan friendly
Tags/catagories/collections: Brands, Face Makeup, Makeup, Primer /Makeup Base, Setting Spray & Powder, Too Faced
Image Alt Text: Hangover Replenishing Face Primer - Too Faced

Title: Hangover Good To Go Skin Protecting Moisturizer SPF25
Description:
Hangover Good to Go Skin Protecting SPF 25 Moisturizer protects, giving you the hydrated, glowing complexion you want while shielding you from harmful UVA/UVB rays with broad-spectrum SPF 25 protection. This lightweight, dewy moisturizer is your daily source of antioxidants, vitamin-enriched moisture, and sun protection.

Too Faced has taken the replenishing and soothing essence of their iconic Hangover Primer to the next level with this lightweight moisturizer with a heavyweight defense created specifically to hydrate and protect your skin while helping your makeup look better.

The formula is infused with a blend of nature¿s hydrators, along with skin loving ingredients like Cinnamon Bark extract, Jojoba Oil, Aloe Vera extract, coconut water, and skin care star Hyaluronic Acid to help nourish skin. The powerful non-greasy formula, with vitamins E, C, and pre-and-probiotic-based ingredients, provides broad-spectrum UVA/UVB SPF 25 protection.

Benefits:
Moisturizes and deeply nourishes skin
Gives skin a luminous glow
Creates a soft, smooth canvas perfect for makeup

Description:
A weightless 3-in-1 mist that primes, sets and refreshes makeup while it helps keep skin hydrated. This super-hydrating, multitasking mist is infused with coconut water and can be used as a primer before makeup, a setting spray to keep makeup in place all day and a midday refresher anytime your skin needs a boost, serving as the perfect cure for a beauty hangover. Title: Born This Way Foundation
Description:
Too Faced Born This Way Undetectable Medium-to-Full Coverage Foundation is an oil-free foundation offering medium-to-full natural coverage.

Inspired by "I woke up like this" perfection, Too Faced Co-founder and Chief Creative Officer Jerrod Blandino set out on a mission to create a foundation so undetectable you can go ahead and lie with beautifully natural coverage that will have everyone thinking you were Born This Way.

Infused with:
Coconut Water: Aids in delicately replenishing skin's moisture levels
Alpine Rose: Helps empower skin's health and resilience
Hyaluronic Acid: Gives a smoother, more youthful appearance

This oil-free foundation masterfully diffuses the line between makeup and skin.

Coverage so undetectable, they'll think you were Born This Way.

Tip: For "I Woke Up Like This" perfection, apply from center of the face outward and blend. Build to full coverage by layering as needed.

Results:
100% said this foundation blurred their imperfections
100% said this foundation made their skin look absolutely perfect
97% said this foundation provided natural coverage

Longwearing
Photo friendly/No flashback

Title: Diamond Light Highlighter Fancy Pink Diamond
Description:
Too Faced Diamond Light Highlighter is a luminous finish highlighter with light-reflecting pearls.

This one-of-a-kind highlighter is infused with real crushed diamond powder and light reflecting pearls for a brilliant glow that will have you on planet shimmer. Light up your complexion with pure radiance in a silky powder formula by swirling the dual-tone, opalescent shades together.

Each highlighter is created with Too Faced's unique marble-pouring technique ensuring no two highlighters will ever look the same - just like a real diamond.

Benefits:
  • Prismatic highlighter infused with real crushed diamond powder and light-reflecting pearls for extra luxe, blinding shimmer
  • Dual-tone shades shift with light and movement
  • Buildable payoff for a customized highlight
  • Loaded with dual-tone pigments for an intense strobing effect
  • Cruelty free

Title: All Nighter Ultra Matte Setting Spray
Description:
A weightless setting spray that locks makeup in place while absorbing oil on the skin's surface and controlling shine for an ultra-matte finish that lasts up to 16 hours.

All Nighter Ultra Matte Setting Sprays micro fine mist refreshes skin while mattifying and setting your look. No makeup meltdowns here Ultra Matte's breathable formula keeps makeup looking shine-free and fresh for up to 16 hours without fading or settling into fine lines. So sweat, get wet, and go to the after party no touch-ups needed.

If you see white droplets on your skin after you spray, thats just the kaolin clay and ultra-mattifying effect at work! Shake the bottle 5 times to activate the formula, then prime it by pressing fully down on the pump and spraying it in the air a few times. This ensures even and translucent application.
Tags/catagories/collections: Brands, Face Makeup, Makeup, Primer /Makeup Base, Setting Spray & Powder, Urban Decay, xpromo20, xpromo30
Image Alt Text: All Nighter Ultra Matte Setting Spray - Urban Decay

Title: ALL NIGHTER SETTING SPRAY
Description:
Is makeup meltdown ruining your midnight mojo? Mist on this weightless spray to give your makeup serious staying power. All Nighter Makeup Setting Spray keeps makeup looking gorgeously just-applied for up to 16 hours without melting, fading or settling into fine lines.

Developed in an exclusive partnership with Skindinavia, our groundbreaking, tested formula is suitable for all skin types, free of oil and parabens, and features patented Temperature Control Technology. Yep, this baby actually lowers the temperature of your makeup to keep foundation, eyeshadow, blush and concealer in place even in hot and humid or cold and windy conditions. The result? Smoother-looking skin and vibrant makeup that lasts all day (or all night).

Title: ALL NIGHTER FACE PRIMER
Description:
A longwear complexion primer that boosts your foundation staying power so it looks fresh for up to 8 hours.

The latest addition to the All Nighter family, this primer goes on sheer and lightweight, making it easy to wear alone or under foundation. It preps skin, giving it a lifted feel and a hit of hydration. By helping to reduce fine lines and erase the appearance of pores, All Nighter is a no-brainer step in your skin prep routine.

Description:
The number-one primer for indestructible, all-day eyeshadow, our legendary Eyeshadow Primer Potion delivers everything you could possibly want in an eye primer: No creasing. More vibrant color. Smoother application.

Eyeshadow Primer Potion features space-age polymer technology that fills in any imperfections on the skin surface, prepping your lids for ALL-day shadow. Of course, every shade is paraben-free.

Description:

Title: Party Favor Moondust Palette
Description:
Feed your glitter addiction with our Party Favor Moondust Palette perfect for a night out.

Each shade is laced with micro-fine sparkle and lush 3D metallic glitter for a luxe, diamond-like effect. Rose-hued shades like Sugar High and Long Night create a subtle flush, while the silver and gold metallics of Neon Moon and No Shame add an icy pop to inner corners.

Sweep shadow along lids, wet as eyeliner, and for the ultimate highlight, dust on cheekbones and there's definitely enough party favors to go around.

Title: Naked Honey Eyeshadow Palette
Description:
Meet the Naked Honey Eyeshadow Palette, our newest addition to the Naked family raw and sticky sweet, just the way nature intended. The irresistible combo of retro glam and golden glow makes this the one palette you'll be craving all year. Get hooked on this buzzed-about palette and its 12 exclusive shades; they perfect for creating a swarm of looks, from bright and sunny to dangerously seductive after dark.

Reach for our go-to shade Amber (it practically glows), create the perfect hazy, smoked-out eye with Sting (warm brown matte), or get hooked on Honey (intense gold metallic) for the ultimate  statement eye.

From daytime matte to sultry metallic looks, blending your best look is easy, since the Naked Honey Eyeshadow Palette comes with a vegan and cruelty-free double-ended brush. One end is a smudger brush, which is short and densely packed to apply shadow along the lower lash line or smudge and blend. The other end is a tapered crease brush, perfect for defining the crease and blending shades. You wont find another palette that this sweet.

Title: Touche Eclat Le Cushion Liquid Foundation Compact SPF50/PA+++
Description:
Yves Saint Laurent Touche Eclat Le Cushion Liquid Foundation Compact SPF50 / PA+++ has the following features:
Thanks to this first cushion foundation with a customisable light and coverage, it offers a burst of brilliant luminosity tailored-made to the unique needs of women across the globe.
Built with a breakthrough network of fibres with bi-material sponge formed of two distinct sides for a customised complexion finish, like an adaptable dimmer switch for your skin.

Title: Concealer Full Coverage 16H Wear
Description:
Yves Saint Laurent All Hours Concealer Full Coverage 16H Wear has the following features:
Instantly blurs and erases imperfections including dark circles, bags, redness, hyperpigmentation, broken capillaries, age spots and discoloration accurately with the soft applicator.
The advanced 16-hour formula will not cake, crease or fade nor will it accentuate the look of fine lines and wrinkles.
The highly concentrated, move-with-you flexible pigments provide a highly workable and blendable texture that stands up to makeup meltdowns and resists fading, heat, humidity and touch.
